description:
Inside The Jazz Note - Jazz House Kids 5th Annual Masterclass, Concert and Conversation featuring Jazz Luminaries Chick Corea and Christian McBride and the Jazz House Big Band. 

Chick Corea spent an afternoon with over 300 NJ music students at SOPAC and an evening concert and conversation with Christian McBride in front of a full house.
Inside The Jazz Note is an annual event produced and presented by Jazz House Kids. Past guests include Pat Metheny, Chris Botti and Esperanza Spalding. 
Sponsored in part by the National Endowment for the Arts and the New Jersey State Council On The Arts.
title: Chick Corea & Christian McBride "Inside The Jazz Note"
